= Emojis

Emoji support allows you to include emoji characters in your documents.

== Basic Emojis

This paragraph contains :smile: emoji.

This paragraph has :heart: and :star: emojis.

== Common Emojis

:thumbsup: Good job!

:thumbsdown: Not recommended.

:warning: Important notice.

:check: Task completed.

== Emojis with Text

The status is :green_circle: online.

The status is :red_circle: offline.

== Emojis in Lists

* :check: First item
* :check: Second item
* :x: Third item (not done)

== Emojis with Other Formatting

This paragraph has :smile: and *bold* text.

This paragraph has :heart: and _italic_ text.

